<img data-attachment-id="158325" data-permalink="https://www.newframe.com/burials-bring-more-pain-for-durban-flood-victims/april-2022-prayers-during-the-funeral-photograph-by-madelene-cronje/" data-orig-file="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KZN-floods_va008.jpg" data-orig-size="2362,1575" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;3.2&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;ILCE-7RM3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;April 2022: Prayers during the funeral. Photograph by Madelene Cronj\u00e9&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1650795057&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;48&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1000&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.008&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;April 2022: Prayers during the funeral. Photograph by Madelene Cronj\u00e9&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KZN-floods_va008-960x640.jpg" data-large-file="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KZN-floods_va008-1440x960.jpg" loading="lazy" width="2362" height="1575" data-id="158325"  src="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KZN-floods_va008.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-158325" srcset="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KZN-floods_va008.jpg 2362w, https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KZN-floods_va008-960x640.jpg 960w, https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KZN-floods_va008-1440x960.jpg 1440w, https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KZN-floods_va008-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KZN-floods_va008-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KZN-floods_va008-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KZN-floods_va008-1920x1280.jpg 1920w, https://www.newframe.